{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879253259,"sessionID":"ses_28559b781ffeNc94rCoz90JPV3","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa6ecf8001GbsP5tQVgU0p96","messageID":"msg_d7aa6cde3001diMC7Pmd3w0yul","sessionID":"ses_28559b781ffeNc94rCoz90JPV3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b46de18ccb584e79a6d1d7ca881d51e3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型增强\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: 本文档针对 AgentCube CLI 项目中的 MetadataService 和数据模型进行架构增强提案。该提案旨在改进元数据管理、验证机制、数据模型的扩展性以及与 Kubernetes CRD 的集成能力。\n6: \n7: ## 背景\n8: \n9: 当前 AgentCube CLI 项目已经实现了基础的元数据管理功能，包括：\n10: \n11: - `AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型（包含20+字段）\n12: - `MetadataService` 用于加载、保存和验证元数据\n13: - 支持 YAML 格式的元数据持久化\n14: - 与 Kubernetes AgentRuntime CRD 的集成\n15: \n16: 然而，在代码审查和实际使用中发现了一些需要改进的方面：\n17: \n18: 1. **数据验证不够完善**：部分字段的验证逻辑分散，缺乏统一的验证框架\n19: 2. **扩展性受限**：添加新字段或自定义元数据需要修改核心模型\n20: 3. **状态管理不清晰**：元数据中的状态字段（如 `agent_id`, `k8s_deployment`）缺乏明确的状态机\n21: 4. **向后兼容性**：元数据格式变更可能导致兼容性问题\n22: 5. **多环境支持**：缺乏对不同部署环境（开发、测试、生产）的元数据隔离\n23: \n24: ## 当前实现分析\n25: \n26: ### MetadataService 现状\n27: \n28: ```python\n29: class MetadataService:\n30:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n31:     def load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n32:     def save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None: ...\n33:     def update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n34:     def validate_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path) -> bool: ...\n35: ```\n36: \n37: ### AgentMetadata 模型现状\n38: \n39: 当前包含以下主要字段：\n40: - 基本信息：`agent_name`, `description`, `language`\n41: - 运行时配置：`entrypoint`, `port`, `build_mode`\n42: - 部署信息：`region`, `version`, `image`\n43: - 认证信息：`auth`, `registry_url`, `registry_username`, `registry_password`\n44: - Kubernetes 集成：`k8s_deployment`, `agent_id`\n45: - URL 配置：`agent_endpoint`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`\n46: - 探针配置：`readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port`\n47: \n48: ## 问题陈述\n49: \n50: ### 1. 验证逻辑分散\n51: \n52: 当前的验证逻辑分散在多个地方：\n53: - Pydantic 模型中的验证器\n54: - MetadataService 中的验证方法\n55: - Runtime 类中的验证调用\n56: \n57: 这导致：\n58: - 难以维护和调试\n59: - 验证规则不一致\n60: - 错误信息不统一\n61: \n62: ### 2. 状态管理混乱\n63: \n64: 元数据包含多种状态字段：\n65: - `agent_id`: AgentCube 分配的 ID\n66: - `version`: 语义版本\n67: - `k8s_deployment`: Kubernetes 部署信息\n68: - `session_id`: 会话 ID\n69: \n70: 这些字段之间缺乏明确的状态转换规则和依赖关系。\n71: \n72: ### 3. 扩展性不足\n73: \n74: 当需要添加新的元数据字段时，必须修改核心模型，这可能导致：\n75: - 破坏向后兼容性\n76: - 增加核心模型的复杂度\n77: - 难以支持插件化的扩展\n78: \n79: ### 4. 配置管理复杂\n80: \n81: 不同环境（开发、测试、生产）需要不同的配置，但当前缺乏：\n82: - 环境配置隔离\n83: - 配置覆盖机制\n84: - 敏感信息保护\n85: \n86: ## 提案方案\n87: \n88: ### 1. 重构验证框架\n89: \n90: #### 1.1 统一验证器接口\n91: \n92: ```python\n93: from abc import ABC, abstractmethod\n94: \n95: class MetadataValidator(ABC):\n96:     \"\"\"元数据验证器基类\"\"\"\n97:     \n98:     @abstractmethod\n99:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> ValidationResult:\n100:         \"\"\"验证元数据并返回结果\"\"\"\n101:         pass\n102: \n103: class ValidationResult:\n104:     \"\"\"验证结果\"\"\"\n105:     def __init__(self, is_valid: bool, errors: List[str] = None, warnings: List[str] = None):\n106:         self.is_valid = is_valid\n107:         self.errors = errors or []\n108:         self.warnings = warnings or []\n109:     \n110:     def add_error(self, error: str) -> None:\n111:         self.errors.append(error)\n112:         self.is_valid = False\n113:     \n114:     def add_warning(self, warning: str) -> None:\n115:         self.warnings.append(warning)\n116: ```\n117: \n118: #### 1.2 具体验证器实现\n119: \n120: ```python\n121: class BasicInfoValidator(MetadataValidator):\n122:     \"\"\"基本信息验证器\"\"\"\n123:     \n124:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> ValidationResult:\n125:         result = ValidationResult(is_valid=True)\n126:         \n127:         if not metadata.agent_name or len(metadata.agent_name) < 2:\n128:             result.add_error(\"agent_name must be at least 2 characters\")\n129:         \n130:         if metadata.language not in [\"python\", \"java\"]:\n131:             result.add_error(f\"Unsupported language: {metadata.language}\")\n132:         \n133:         if not (1 <= metadata.port <= 65535):\n134:             result.add_error(\"port must be between 1 and 65535\")\n135:         \n136:         return result\n137: \n138: class DeploymentValidator(MetadataValidator):\n139:     \"\"\"部署配置验证器\"\"\"\n140:     \n141:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> ValidationResult:\n142:         result = ValidationResult(is_valid=True)\n143:         \n144:         if metadata.build_mode not in [\"local\", \"cloud\"]:\n145:             result.add_error(f\"Invalid build_mode: {metadata.build_mode}\")\n146:         \n147:         if metadata.build_mode == \"cloud\" and not metadata.cloud_provider:\n148:             result.add_warning(\"cloud_provider is recommended for cloud builds\")\n149:         \n150:         return result\n151: \n152: class KubernetesValidator(MetadataValidator):\n153:     \"\"\"Kubernetes 配置验证器\"\"\"\n154:     \n155:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> ValidationResult:\n156:         result = ValidationResult(is_valid=True)\n157:         \n158:         if metadata.k8s_deployment:\n159:             deployment = metadata.k8s_deployment\n160:             if deployment.get(\"type\") == \"AgentRuntime\":\n161:                 if not metadata.router_url:\n162:                     result.add_error(\"router_url is required for AgentRuntime deployments\")\n163:                 if not metadata.workload_manager_url:\n164:                     result.add_error(\"workload_manager_url is required for AgentRuntime deployments\")\n165:         \n166:         return result\n167: ```\n168: \n169: #### 1.3 验证链模式\n170: \n171: ```python\n172: class MetadataValidationChain:\n173:     \"\"\"元数据验证链\"\"\"\n174:     \n175:     def __init__(self):\n176:         self.validators: List[MetadataValidator] = []\n177:         self.add_default_validators()\n178:     \n179:     def add_default_validators(self) -> None:\n180:         \"\"\"添加默认验证器\"\"\"\n181:         self.validators.extend([\n182:             BasicInfoValidator(),\n183:             DeploymentValidator(),\n184:             KubernetesValidator(),\n185:             WorkspaceValidator(),\n186:         ])\n187:     \n188:     def add_validator(self, validator: MetadataValidator) -> None:\n189:         \"\"\"添加自定义验证器\"\"\"\n190:         self.validators.append(validator)\n191:     \n192:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> ValidationResult:\n193:         \"\"\"执行所有验证\"\"\"\n194:         final_result = ValidationResult(is_valid=True)\n195:         \n196:         for validator in self.validators:\n197:             result = validator.validate(metadata)\n198:             final_result.errors.extend(result.errors)\n199:             final_result.warnings.extend(result.warnings)\n200:             if not result.is_valid:\n201:                 final_result.is_valid = False\n202:         \n203:         return final_result\n204: ```\n205: \n206: ### 2. 状态机管理\n207: \n208: #### 2.1 定义状态模型\n209: \n210: ```python\n211: from enum import Enum\n212: from typing import Optional, Dict, Any\n213: from datetime import datetime\n214: \n215: class AgentState(str, Enum):\n216:     \"\"\"代理状态\"\"\"\n217:     UNINITIALIZED = \"uninitialized\"\n218:     PACKAGED = \"packaged\"\n219:     BUILT = \"built\"\n220:     PUBLISHED = \"published\"\n221:     RUNNING = \"running\"\n222:     STOPPED = \"stopped\"\n223:     ERROR = \"error\"\n224: \n225: class AgentStateMachine:\n226:     \"\"\"代理状态机\"\"\"\n227:     \n228:     # 定义状态转换\n229:     TRANSITIONS = {\n230:         AgentState.UNINITIALIZED: [AgentState.PACKAGED],\n231:         AgentState.PACKAGED: [AgentState.BUILT],\n232:         AgentState.BUILT: [AgentState.PUBLISHED, AgentState.ERROR],\n233:         AgentState.PUBLISHED: [AgentState.RUNNING, AgentState.ERROR],\n234:         AgentState.RUNNING: [AgentState.STOPPED, AgentState.ERROR],\n235:         AgentState.STOPPED: [AgentState.RUNNING],\n236:         AgentState.ERROR: [AgentState.PACKAGED, AgentState.BUILT],\n237:     }\n238:     \n239:     @classmethod\n240:     def can_transition(cls, from_state: AgentState, to_state: AgentState) -> bool:\n241:         \"\"\"检查状态转换是否允许\"\"\"\n242:         return to_state in cls.TRANSITIONS.get(from_state, [])\n243:     \n244:     @classmethod\n245:     def validate_transition(cls, from_state: AgentState, to_state: AgentState) -> None:\n246:         \"\"\"验证状态转换，如果不允许则抛出异常\"\"\"\n247:         if not cls.can_transition(from_state, to_state):\n248:             raise ValueError(\n249:                 f\"Invalid state transition from {from_state} to {to_state}. \"\n250:                 f\"Allowed transitions: {cls.TRANSITIONS.get(from_state, [])}\"\n251:             )\n252: ```\n253: \n254: #### 2.2 扩展元数据模型\n255: \n256: ```python\n257: class AgentMetadata(BaseModel):\n258:     \"\"\"增强的代理元数据模型\"\"\"\n259:     \n260:     # ... 现有字段 ...\n261:     \n262:     # 新增状态管理字段\n263:     state: AgentState = AgentState.UNINITIALIZED\n264:     state_transitions: List[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default_factory=list)\n265:     \n266:     # 新增时间戳\n267:     created_at: Optional[datetime] = None\n268:     updated_at: Optional[datetime] = None\n269:     \n270:     # 新增环境配置\n271:     environment: str = \"development\"  # development, testing, production\n272:     environment_overrides: Dict[str, Any] = Field(default_factory=dict)\n273:     \n274:     def transition_to(self, new_state: AgentState) -> None:\n275:         \"\"\"执行状态转换\"\"\"\n276:         AgentStateMachine.validate_transition(self.state, new_state)\n277:         \n278:         # 记录状态转换\n279:         self.state_transitions.append({\n280:             \"from\": self.state,\n281:             \"to\": new_state,\n282:             \"timestamp\": datetime.utcnow().isoformat(),\n283:         })\n284:         \n285:         self.state = new_state\n286:         self.updated_at = datetime.utcnow()\n287:     \n288:     def get_effective_config(self) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n289:         \"\"\"获取有效的配置（应用环境覆盖）\"\"\"\n290:         base_config = self.model_dump(exclude_none=True)\n291:         base_config.pop(\"environment_overrides\", None)\n292:         base_config.pop(\"state_transitions\", None)\n293:         \n294:         # 应用环境覆盖\n295:         overrides = self.environment_overrides.get(self.environment, {})\n296:         return {**base_config, **overrides}\n297: ```\n298: \n299: ### 3. 扩展性增强\n300: \n301: #### 3.1 自定义元数据支持\n302: \n303: ```python\n304: class CustomMetadata(BaseModel):\n305:     \"\"\"自定义元数据扩展\"\"\"\n306:     \n307:     custom_fields: Dict[str, Any] = Field(default_factory=dict)\n308:     \n309:     def get_field(self, key: str, default: Any = None) -> Any:\n310:         \"\"\"获取自定义字段\"\"\"\n311:         return self.custom_fields.get(key, default)\n312:     \n313:     def set_field(self, key: str, value: Any) -> None:\n314:         \"\"\"设置自定义字段\"\"\"\n315:         self.custom_fields[key] = value\n316:     \n317:     def remove_field(self, key: str) -> None:\n318:         \"\"\"移除自定义字段\"\"\"\n319:         self.custom_fields.pop(key, None)\n320: \n321: # 扩展 AgentMetadata\n322: class AgentMetadata(BaseModel):\n323:     # ... 现有字段 ...\n324:     custom_metadata: Optional[CustomMetadata] = None\n325: ```\n326: \n327: #### 3.2 插件系统\n328: \n329: ```python\n330: class MetadataPlugin(ABC):\n331:     \"\"\"元数据插件基类\"\"\"\n332:     \n333:     @property\n334:     @abstractmethod\n335:     def name(self) -> str:\n336:         \"\"\"插件名称\"\"\"\n337:         pass\n338:     \n339:     @abstractmethod\n340:     def before_save(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n341:         \"\"\"保存前的钩子\"\"\"\n342:         pass\n343:     \n344:     @abstractmethod\n345:     def after_load(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n346:         \"\"\"加载后的钩子\"\"\"\n347:         pass\n348:     \n349:     @abstractmethod\n350:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> List[str]:\n351:         \"\"\"验证元数据，返回错误列表\"\"\"\n352:         pass\n353: \n354: class MetadataPluginManager:\n355:     \"\"\"元数据插件管理器\"\"\"\n356:     \n357:     def __init__(self):\n358:         self.plugins: List[MetadataPlugin] = []\n359:     \n360:     def register_plugin(self, plugin: MetadataPlugin) -> None:\n361:         \"\"\"注册插件\"\"\"\n362:         self.plugins.append(plugin)\n363:     \n364:     def unregister_plugin(self, plugin_name: str) -> None:\n365:         \"\"\"注销插件\"\"\"\n366:         self.plugins = [p for p in self.plugins if p.name != plugin_name]\n367:     \n368:     def before_save(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n369:         \"\"\"执行所有插件的保存前钩子\"\"\"\n370:         for plugin in self.plugins:\n371:             plugin.before_save(metadata)\n372:     \n373:     def after_load(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n374:         \"\"\"执行所有插件的加载后钩子\"\"\"\n375:         for plugin in self.plugins:\n376:             plugin.after_load(metadata)\n377:     \n378:     def validate(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> List[str]:\n379:         \"\"\"执行所有插件的验证\"\"\"\n380:         all_errors = []\n381:         for plugin in self.plugins:\n382:             errors = plugin.validate(metadata)\n383:             all_errors.extend(errors)\n384:         return all_errors\n385: ```\n386: \n387: ### 4. 配置管理增强\n388: \n389: #### 4.1 多环境配置\n390: \n391: ```python\n392: class EnvironmentConfig(BaseModel):\n393:     \"\"\"环境配置\"\"\"\n394:     \n395:     name: str\n396:     registry_url: Optional[str] = None\n397:     registry_username: Optional[str] = None\n398:     registry_password: Optional[str] = None\n399:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = None\n400:     region: Optional[str] = None\n401:     workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None\n402:     router_url: Optional[str] = None\n403:     namespace: str = \"default\"\n404:     replicas: int = 1\n405:     \n406:     @classmethod\n407:     def from_dict(cls, env_name: str, config: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"EnvironmentConfig\":\n408:         \"\"\"从字典创建环境配置\"\"\"\n409:         return cls(name=env_name, **config)\n410: \n411: class ConfigManager:\n412:     \"\"\"配置管理器\"\"\"\n413:     \n414:     DEFAULT_ENVIRONMENTS = {\n415:         \"development\": {\n416:             \"registry_url\": \"localhost:5000\",\n417:             \"namespace\": \"dev\",\n418:         },\n419:         \"testing\": {\n420:             \"namespace\": \"test\",\n421:         },\n422:         \"production\": {\n423:             \"replicas\": 3,\n424:         },\n425:     }\n426:     \n427:     def __init__(self, config_path: Optional[Path] = None):\n428:         self.environments: Dict[str, EnvironmentConfig] = {}\n429:         self._load_default_environments()\n430:         if config_path:\n431:             self._load_from_file(config_path)\n432:     \n433:     def _load_default_environments(self) -> None:\n434:         \"\"\"加载默认环境配置\"\"\"\n435:         for env_name, config in self.DEFAULT_ENVIRONMENTS.items():\n436:             self.environments[env_name] = EnvironmentConfig.from_dict(env_name, config)\n437:     \n438:     def _load_from_file(self, config_path: Path) -> None:\n439:         \"\"\"从文件加载环境配置\"\"\"\n440:         if config_path.exists():\n441:             import yaml\n442:             with open(config_path, \"r\") as f:\n443:                 config_data = yaml.safe_load(f) or {}\n444:                 for env_name, env_config in config_data.get(\"environments\", {}).items():\n445:                     self.environments[env_name] = EnvironmentConfig.from_dict(env_name, env_config)\n446:     \n447:     def get_environment(self, env_name: str) -> EnvironmentConfig:\n448:         \"\"\"获取环境配置\"\"\"\n449:         if env_name not in self.environments:\n450:             raise ValueError(f\"Environment not found: {env_name}\")\n451:         return self.environments[env_name]\n452:     \n453:     def apply_environment_config(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, env_name: str) -> AgentMetadata:\n454:         \"\"\"应用环境配置到元数据\"\"\"\n455:         env_config = self.get_environment(env_name)\n456:         \n457:         # 更新元数据字段\n458:         if env_config.registry_url:\n459:             metadata.registry_url = env_config.registry_url\n460:         if env_config.registry_username:\n461:             metadata.registry_username = env_config.registry_username\n462:         if env_config.registry_password:\n463:             metadata.registry_password = env_config.registry_password\n464:         if env_config.cloud_provider:\n465:             metadata.cloud_provider = env_config.cloud_provider\n466:         if env_config.region:\n467:             metadata.region = env_config.region\n468:         if env_config.workload_manager_url:\n469:             metadata.workload_manager_url = env_config.workload_manager_url\n470:         if env_config.router_url:\n471:             metadata.router_url = env_config.router_url\n472:         \n473:         metadata.environment = env_name\n474:         return metadata\n475: ```\n476: \n477: #### 4.2 敏感信息保护\n478: \n479: ```python\n480: from cryptography.fernet import Fernet\n481: import base64\n482: import os\n483: \n484: class SensitiveDataManager:\n485:     \"\"\"敏感信息管理器\"\"\"\n486:     \n487:     def __init__(self, key: Optional[bytes] = None):\n488:         \"\"\"初始化加密管理器\n489:         \n490:         Args:\n491:             key: 加密密钥，如果为 None 则从环境变量获取或生成新密钥\n492:         \"\"\"\n493:         if key is None:\n494:             key = self._get_or_create_key()\n495:         self.cipher = Fernet(key)\n496:     \n497:     def _get_or_create_key(self) -> bytes:\n498:         \"\"\"获取或创建加密密钥\"\"\"\n499:         key_str = os.environ.get(\"AGENTCUBE_ENCRYPTION_KEY\")\n500:         if key_str:\n501:             return base64.urlsafe_b64decode(key_str.encode())\n502:         else:\n503:             key = Fernet.generate_key()\n504:             os.environ[\"AGENTCUBE_ENCRYPTION_KEY\"] = base64.urlsafe_b64encode(key).decode()\n505:             return key\n506:     \n507:     def encrypt(self, data: str) -> str:\n508:         \"\"\"加密数据\"\"\"\n509:         encrypted = self.cipher.encrypt(data.encode())\n510:         return base64.urlsafe_b64encode(encrypted).decode()\n511:     \n512:     def decrypt(self, encrypted_data: str) -> str:\n513:         \"\"\"解密数据\"\"\"\n514:         encrypted = base64.urlsafe_b64decode(encrypted_data.encode())\n515:         decrypted = self.cipher.decrypt(encrypted)\n516:         return decrypted.decode()\n517:     \n518:     def encrypt_field(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, field_name: str) -> None:\n519:         \"\"\"加密元数据中的敏感字段\"\"\"\n520:         field_value = getattr(metadata, field_name, None)\n521:         if field_value:\n522:             setattr(metadata, field_name, self.encrypt(field_value))\n523:     \n524:     def decrypt_field(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, field_name: str) -> str:\n525:         \"\"\"解密元数据中的敏感字段\"\"\"\n526:         field_value = getattr(metadata, field_name, None)\n527:         if field_value:\n528:             return self.decrypt(field_value)\n529:         return \"\"\n530: ```\n531: \n532: ### 5. 重构后的 MetadataService\n533: \n534: ```python\n535: class MetadataService:\n536:     \"\"\"增强的元数据服务\"\"\"\n537:     \n538:     def __init__(\n539:         self,\n540:         verbose: bool = False,\n541:         config_manager: Optional[ConfigManager] = None,\n542:         plugin_manager: Optional[MetadataPluginManager] = None,\n543:         sensitive_data_manager: Optional[SensitiveDataManager] = None,\n544:     ) -> None:\n545:         self.verbose = verbose\n546:         self.config_manager = config_manager or ConfigManager()\n547:         self.plugin_manager = plugin_manager or MetadataPluginManager()\n548:         self.sensitive_data_manager = sensitive_data_manager\n549:         self.validation_chain = MetadataValidationChain()\n550:         \n551:         self.logger = get_logger(self.__class__.__name__)\n552:     \n553:     def load_metadata(\n554:         self,\n555:         workspace_path: Path,\n556:         environment: Optional[str] = None,\n557:         decrypt_sensitive: bool = True,\n558:     ) -> AgentMetadata:\n559:         \"\"\"加载元数据\n560:         \n561:         Args:\n562:             workspace_path: 工作空间路径\n563:             environment: 环境名称，如果提供则应用环境配置\n564:             decrypt_sensitive: 是否解密敏感字段\n565:             \n566:         Returns:\n567:             AgentMetadata: 加载的元数据\n568:         \"\"\"\n569:         metadata_file = self._find_metadata_file(workspace_path)\n570:         \n571:         with open(metadata_file, \"r\") as f:\n572:             metadata_dict = yaml.safe_load(f)\n573:         \n574:         metadata = AgentMetadata(**metadata_dict)\n575:         \n576:         # 解密敏感字段\n577:         if decrypt_sensitive and self.sensitive_data_manager:\n578:             for field in [\"registry_password\", \"image_password\"]:\n579:                 encrypted_value = getattr(metadata, field, None)\n580:                 if encrypted_value and encrypted_value.startswith(\"encrypted:\"):\n581:                     decrypted_value = self.sensitive_data_manager.decrypt(\n582:                         encrypted_value.replace(\"encrypted:\", \"\", 1)\n583:                     )\n584:                     setattr(metadata, field, decrypted_value)\n585:         \n586:         # 应用环境配置\n587:         if environment:\n588:             metadata = self.config_manager.apply_environment_config(metadata, environment)\n589:         \n590:         # 执行插件加载后钩子\n591:         self.plugin_manager.after_load(metadata)\n592:         \n593:         # 验证元数据\n594:         validation_result = self.validation_chain.validate(metadata)\n595:         if not validation_result.is_valid:\n596:             error_msg = \"Metadata validation failed:\\n\" + \"\\n\".join(validation_result.errors)\n597:             self.logger.error(error_msg)\n598:             raise ValueError(error_msg)\n599:         \n600:         if validation_result.warnings:\n601:             self.logger.warning(\n602:                 \"Metadata validation warnings:\\n\" + \"\\n\".join(validation_result.warnings)\n603:             )\n604:         \n605:         return metadata\n606:     \n607:     def save_metadata(\n608:         self,\n609:         workspace_path: Path,\n610:         metadata: AgentMetadata,\n611:         encrypt_sensitive: bool = True,\n612:     ) -> None:\n613:         \"\"\"保存元数据\n614:         \n615:         Args:\n616:             workspace_path: 工作空间路径\n617:             metadata: 要保存的元数据\n618:             encrypt_sensitive: 是否加密敏感字段\n619:         \"\"\"\n620:         # 执行插件保存前钩子\n621:         self.plugin_manager.before_save(metadata)\n622:         \n623:         # 验证元数据\n624:         validation_result = self.validation_chain.validate(metadata)\n625:         if not validation_result.is_valid:\n626:             error_msg = \"Metadata validation failed:\\n\" + \"\\n\".join(validation_result.errors)\n627:             raise ValueError(error_msg)\n628:         \n629:         # 加密敏感字段\n630:         if encrypt_sensitive and self.sensitive_data_manager:\n631:             for field in [\"registry_password\", \"image_password\"]:\n632:                 field_value = getattr(metadata, field, None)\n633:                 if field_value and not field_value.startswith(\"encrypted:\"):\n634:                     encrypted_value = self.sensitive_data_manager.encrypt(field_value)\n635:                     setattr(metadata, field, f\"encrypted:{encrypted_value}\")\n636:         \n637:         # 更新时间戳\n638:         if metadata.created_at is None:\n639:             metadata.created_at = datetime.utcnow()\n640:         metadata.updated_at = datetime.utcnow()\n641:         \n642:         # 保存到文件\n643:         metadata_file = workspace_path / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\n644:         metadata_dict = metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True)\n645:         \n646:         with open(metadata_file, \"w\") as f:\n647:             yaml.dump(metadata_dict, f, default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)\n648:         \n649:         self.logger.info(f\"Metadata saved to {metadata_file}\")\n650:     \n651:     def update_metadata(\n652:         self,\n653:         workspace_path: Path,\n654:         updates: Dict[str, Any],\n655:         transition_to: Optional[AgentState] = None,\n656:     ) -> AgentMetadata:\n657:         \"\"\"更新元数据\n658:         \n659:         Args:\n660:             workspace_path: 工作空间路径\n661:             updates: 更新内容的字典\n662:             transition_to: 可选的状态转换\n663:             \n664:         Returns:\n665:             AgentMetadata: 更新后的元数据\n666:         \"\"\"\n667:         metadata = self.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n668:         \n669:         # 应用更新\n670:         for key, value in updates.items():\n671:             if hasattr(metadata, key):\n672:                 setattr(metadata, key, value)\n673:         \n674:         # 执行状态转换\n675:         if transition_to:\n676:             metadata.transition_to(transition_to)\n677:         \n678:         # 保存更新后的元数据\n679:         self.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n680:         \n681:         return metadata\n682:     \n683:     def validate_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path) -> bool:\n684:         \"\"\"验证工作空间\n685:         \n686:         Args:\n687:             workspace_path: 工作空间路径\n688:             \n689:         Returns:\n690:             bool: 验证是否通过\n691:         \"\"\"\n692:         if not workspace_path.exists() or not workspace_path.is_dir():\n693:             raise ValueError(f\"Workspace directory does not exist: {workspace_path}\")\n694:         \n695:         # 尝试加载元数据\n696:         metadata = self.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n697:         \n698:         # 根据语言验证工作空间结构\n699:         if metadata.language == \"python\":\n700:             self._validate_python_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)\n701:         elif metadata.language == \"java\":\n702:             self._validate_java_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)\n703:         \n704:         return True\n705:     \n706:     def _validate_python_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n707:         \"\"\"验证 Python 工作空间\"\"\"\n708:         python_files = list(workspace_path.glob(\"*.py\"))\n709:         if not python_files:\n710:             raise ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")\n711:         \n712:         requirements_file = metadata.requirements_file or \"requirements.txt\"\n713:         if not (workspace_path / requirements_file).exists():\n714:             self.logger.warning(f\"Requirements file not found: {requirements_file}\")\n715:     \n716:     def _validate_java_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n717:         \"\"\"验证 Java 工作空间\"\"\"\n718:         if not (workspace_path / \"pom.xml\").exists():\n719:             raise ValueError(\"pom.xml not found in workspace\")\n720:     \n721:     def _find_metadata_file(self, workspace_path: Path) -> Path:\n722:         \"\"\"查找元数据文件\"\"\"\n723:         for filename in [\"agent_metadata.yaml\", \"agent.yaml\", \"metadata.yaml\"]:\n724:             metadata_file = workspace_path / filename\n725:             if metadata_file.exists():\n726:                 return metadata_file\n727:         \n728:         raise FileNotFoundError(f\"No metadata file found in {workspace_path}\")\n729: ```\n730: \n731: ## 实施计划\n732: \n733: ### 阶段一：基础框架重构（2周）\n734: \n735: **目标**：建立新的验证框架和状态机\n736: \n737: **任务**：\n738: 1. 实现 `MetadataValidator` 基类和验证器接口\n739: 2. 实现状态机 `AgentStateMachine`\n740: 3. 重构现有的验证逻辑到新的验证器\n741: 4. 添加单元测试覆盖验证框架\n742: \n743: **交付物**：\n744: - 新的验证框架代码\n745: - 状态机实现\n746: - 单元测试覆盖率 > 80%\n747: \n748: ### 阶段二：扩展性增强（1周）\n749: \n750: **目标**：实现插件系统和自定义元数据支持\n751: \n752: **任务**：\n753: 1. 实现 `MetadataPlugin` 基类和插件管理器\n754: 2. 扩展 `AgentMetadata` 支持自定义字段\n755: 3. 实现示例插件（如版本检查、依赖验证）\n756: 4. 编写插件开发文档\n757: \n758: **交付物**：\n759: - 插件系统代码\n760: - 示例插件\n761: - 插件开发文档\n762: \n763: ### 阶段三：配置管理优化（1周）\n764: \n765: **目标**：实现多环境配置和敏感信息保护\n766: \n767: **任务**：\n768: 1. 实现 `ConfigManager` 和环境配置\n769: 2. 实现 `SensitiveDataManager` 和加密功能\n770: 3. 更新 `MetadataService` 集成新功能\n771: 4. 编写配置管理文档\n772: \n773: **交付物**：\n774: - 配置管理代码\n775: - 加密管理代码\n776: - 配置管理文档\n777: \n778: ### 阶段四：集成和测试（1周）\n779: \n780: **目标**：全面集成新功能并进行测试\n781: \n782: **任务**：\n783: 1. 更新所有 Runtime 类使用新的 MetadataService\n784: 2. 编写集成测试\n785: 3. 迁移现有测试用例\n786: 4. 性能测试和优化\n787: \n788: **交付物**：\n789: - 更新的所有 Runtime 类\n790: - 集成测试套件\n791: - 性能测试报告\n792: \n793: ### 阶段五：文档和发布（1周）\n794: \n795: **目标**：完善文档并准备发布\n796: \n797: **任务**：\n798: 1. 更新 API 文档\n799: 2. 编写迁移指南\n800: 3. 编写用户指南\n801: 4. 准备版本发布\n802: \n803: **交付物**：\n804: - 完整的 API 文档\n805: - 迁移指南\n806: - 用户指南\n807: - 版本发布说明\n808: \n809: ## 影响分析\n810: \n811: ### 向后兼容性\n812: \n813: **兼容性保证**：\n814: - 保留所有现有字段和方法\n815: - 元数据文件格式向后兼容\n816: - 旧的验证逻辑逐步迁移\n817: \n818: **迁移策略**：\n819: 1. 保留旧的验证逻辑作为兼容层\n820: 2. 新功能通过配置开关控制\n821: 3. 提供迁移脚本转换旧元数据\n822: \n823: ### 性能影响\n824: \n825: **预期影响**：\n826: - 验证框架：轻微性能提升（优化验证逻辑）\n827: - 加密功能：密码操作增加 10-20ms 延迟\n828: - 插件系统：根据插件数量线性增加\n829: \n830: **优化措施**：\n831: - 延迟加载插件\n832: - 加密操作异步化\n833: - 缓存验证结果\n834: \n835: ### 依赖变更\n836: \n837: **新增依赖**：\n838: - `cryptography`（用于加密功能）\n839: \n840: **版本要求**：\n841: - `pydantic>=2.0.0`（保持不变）\n842: - `pyyaml>=6.0`（保持不变）\n843: \n844: ## 风险评估\n845: \n846: ### 高风险\n847: \n848: 1. **状态转换兼容性**\n849:    - 风险：现有代码依赖隐式状态转换\n850:    - 缓解：保留兼容层，详细日志记录\n851: \n852: 2. **加密密钥管理**\n853:    - 风险：密钥丢失导致数据无法解密\n854:    - 缓解：提供密钥备份和恢复机制\n855: \n856: ### 中风险\n857: \n858: 1. **插件生态系统**\n859:    - 风险：缺乏插件导致扩展能力未充分利用\n860:    - 缓解：提供核心插件集合和开发指南\n861: \n862: 2. **性能回归**\n863:    - 风险：新功能影响 CLI 响应速度\n864:    - 缓解：性能测试和优化\n865: \n866: ### 低风险\n867: \n868: 1. **配置复杂性**\n869:    - 风险：多环境配置增加学习曲线\n870:    - 缓解：提供默认配置和详细文档\n871: \n872: ## 成功指标\n873: \n874: ### 技术指标\n875: \n876: - 单元测试覆盖率 > 85%\n877: - 集成测试覆盖率 > 70%\n878: - 验证响应时间 < 50ms\n879: - 加密操作延迟 < 20ms\n880: \n881: ### 质量指标\n882: \n883: - 代码审查通过率 100%\n884: - 静态分析无严重问题\n885: - 文档完整性 > 90%\n886: \n887: ### 用户体验指标\n888: \n889: - 元数据加载错误率降低 50%\n890: - 配置迁移成功率 > 95%\n891: - 用户满意度调查 > 8/10\n892: \n893: ## 备选方案\n894: \n895: ### 方案 A：最小化改动\n896: \n897: **描述**：仅重构验证逻辑，保持其他功能不变\n898: \n899: **优点**：\n900: - 改动范围小\n901: - 风险低\n902: - 实施快速\n903: \n904: **缺点**：\n905: - 不解决扩展性问题\n906: - 状态管理仍然混乱\n907: - 配置管理未改善\n908: \n909: ### 方案 B：激进重构\n910: \n911: **描述**：完全重写元数据系统，采用新的数据模型\n912: \n913: **优点**：\n914: - 彻底解决现有问题\n915: - 更好的架构设计\n916: - 长期维护成本低\n917: \n918: **缺点**：\n919: - 实施周期长\n920: - 兼容性挑战大\n921: - 风险高\n922: \n923: ### 推荐方案：渐进式增强\n924: \n925: 采用本提案的方案，通过分阶段实施，在保证兼容性的同时逐步增强功能。\n926: \n927: ## 结论\n928: \n929: 本提案通过引入统一的验证框架、状态机管理、插件系统和配置管理增强，显著改善了 MetadataService 和数据模型的架构。该方案在保持向后兼容性的同时，提供了更好的扩展性、可维护性和用户体验。\n930: \n931: 建议按照实施计划分阶段推进，每个阶段都有明确的交付物和验证标准，确保项目质量和进度可控。\n\n(End of file - total 931 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Proposal: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型增强\n\n## 概述\n\n本文档针对 AgentCube CLI 项目中的 MetadataService 和数据模型进行架构增强提案。该提案旨在改进元数据管理、验证机制、数据模型的扩展性以及与 Kubernetes CRD 的集成能力。\n\n## 背景\n\n当前 AgentCube CLI 项目已经实现了基础的元数据管理功能，包括：\n\n- `AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型（包含20+字段）\n- `MetadataService` 用于加载、保存和验证元数据\n- 支持 YAML 格式的元数据持久化\n- 与 Kubernetes AgentRuntime CRD 的集成\n\n然而，在代码审查和实际使用中发现了一些需要改进的方面：\n\n1. **数据验证不够完善**：部分字段的验证逻辑分散，缺乏统一的验证框架\n2. **扩展性受限**：添加新字段或自定义元数据需要修改核心模型\n3. **状态管理不清晰**：元数据中的状态字段（如 `agent_id`, `k8s_deployment`）缺乏明确的状态机","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775879253243,"end":1775879253254}}}}
